### Weekly consumable & equipment list (all pre-organised Friday prior)

| Area    | Items                                                                                                                            |
| ------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| FLA     | Big-book « À l’école » (chart), magnetic names, mini whiteboards, dry-erase markers, flashcards */a / i/*.                       |
| Math    | Foam ten-frames, coloured counters, hula hoops, symbol paddles > < =.                                                            |
| Science | Sound tubes, scent jars (cotton+extract), textured fabrics, kaleidoscopes, sugar/salt tasting dots, thermometer, rain gauge kit. |
| Health  | Glitter-germ lotion, portable UV box, six-step poster, feelings wheels (laminated).                                              |
| Art     | Black crayons, tempera (primary colours), brushes, mirrors, large leaf collection, wax crayons, cardstock, tape.                 |

These **four meticulously-timed days** launch Grade 1 routines while directly evidencing the first required outcomes in French Language Arts, Mathematics (counting to 10), Science (Five Senses), Social Studies (class rules), Health, and Visual Arts. Use them “as-is” or tweak times to fit your specialist schedules next September.

