### Wednesday – “J’entends / Dictée VC”

*Daily why*: reinforce sound-symbol for */e/ /o/* and count backwards 10→0 (Math SCO 1.N.1).

| Time        | Block                                                                                                     | Key moves                                         | Assessment |
| ----------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- | ---------- |
| 08:30-08:45 | Chant feelings + sound review.                                                                            |                                                   |            |
| 08:45-09:15 | **Dictée** 5 VC words (*me, le, la, mi, mo*). Dry-erase boards.                                           | Mark letter formation and phoneme match.          |            |
| 09:15-09:35 | Introduce “Magic Sound Bag” – pull object, ID beginning sound.                                            | ✓ tally correct identifications.                  |            |
| 09:45-10:30 | **Math** – **Backward count relay**: pass plush bear, say next lower number. Use number line for support. | Teacher note: who skips numbers.                  |            |
| 10:45-11:30 | **Science / Maker** – build **Recycled Toy** (cardboard, caps). Focus: strong/weak joints.                | Photograph result; peer praise “one strong part”. |            |
| 12:45-13:25 | **Fire-Safety mini-comic** – Stop/Drop/Roll sequence (3 panels).                                          | Collect comics; reteach if order wrong.           |            |
| 13:25-14:00 | **Art add-on** – colour toy blueprint.                                                                    |                                                   |            |

Prep: replenish dry-erase cloths; gather maker junk; print comic template.

